{
  "abstract": "Use of heterogeneous soil salinity under natural conditions in field screening of genotypes for salinity tolerance is suggested. Methods for advancing breeding material and for testing the end product in a program to breed chickpea and pigeonpea cultivars with increased salinity tolerance are proposed.",
